          "date": "2020-08-25 22:12:22.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-13923 lnet: Add missing lnet_peer_ni_decref call",
        "message": "LU-13923 lnet: Add missing lnet_peer_ni_decref call\n\nThe code added in LU-13606 was missing a refcount decrement.\nThe call to lnet_nid2peerni_locked is incrementing a refcount\non a peer_ni object which is never decremented. This results in LNet\nbeing unable to cleanup properly on \"unconfigure\" or \"net del\"\noperation, causing lnetctl to hang.\n\nFixes: b0e8ab1 (\"LU-13606 lnet: Allow router to forward to healthier NID\")\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ie2614207f3190bbdddbecdef5054b7b76e004859\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
